# Kompservisas — Project Overview

Bilingual (Lithuanian default, English secondary) e-shop and catalogue for used
business-class computers and repair services. Production domain: `kompservisas.lt`.

## Stack

- **Next.js 15** with the **pages router** (`pages/`), ISR via `getStaticProps` + `revalidate`
- **React 19**, **TypeScript 5** (strict)
- **MUI v6** + **Emotion** (`@emotion/react`, `@emotion/styled`) for styling
- **next-i18next** (`lt` default, `en`) — translations in `public/locales/<locale>/<namespace>.json`
- **GraphQL** via `graphql-request` against a **Strapi** backend; types generated by GraphQL Codegen
- **TanStack Query** for client-side data fetching; **react-hook-form** + **yup** for forms
- **next-seo** + **next-sitemap** for SEO; **Partytown** for 3rd-party scripts
- **Vitest** (unit) + **Playwright** (e2e)

## Directory Conventions

- `pages/<route>/index.tsx` — thin Next.js route files: only `getStaticProps` / `getStaticPaths` and a one-line render of the page component from `src/pages/`
- `src/pages/<PageName>/<PageName>.tsx` — page component with logic
- `src/pages/<PageName>/<pageName>Styles.ts` — styles for that page (see `styling` rule)
- `src/components/` — shared components
- `src/constants/`, `src/helpers/`, `src/hooks/`, `src/mixins/`, `src/metaData.ts`, `src/theme.ts`
- `api/generated/` — generated GraphQL types/operations (do NOT edit)
- `api/graphql-hooks.ts` — hand-written hooks wrapping generated operations
- `@types/resources.d.ts` — generated i18n key types (regenerate with `npm run interface`)

## Non-Negotiables

- Keep route files in `pages/` thin; put rendering and logic in `src/pages/`.
- Never edit `api/generated/**` by hand.
- Every user-visible string goes through `useTranslation` / `<Trans>` — no hardcoded copy.
